Name: Vendor neutral sequence (VENUS) acquisition for mtsat.
Description: ISMRM/NIST phantom data acquired using qmrlab/mt_sat sequence v1.0.0 and vendor-native protocols on 1 GE (750) and 2 Siemens scanners (Skyra and Prisma) at 3T. The dataset also contains (non-image) derivatives for 3 healthy participants.
